aliasId.description: (Required) - Alias ID of a bot that is a member of this network of bots.

aliasName.description: (Required) - Alias name of a bot that is a member of this network of bots.

id.description: (Required) - Unique ID of a bot that is a member of this network of bots.

name.description: Name of the bot. The bot name must be unique in the account that creates the bot. Type String. Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 100.

version.description: (Required) - Version of a bot that is a member of this network of bots.
